Description: Advanced tools for analyzing the FDA Adverse Event Reporting
    System (FAERS) data, enhancing drug safety research. Provides
    functions to download cleaned FAERS data and import relational
    datasets, facilitating case identification and control selection to
    address confounding in analyses. Provides functions for descriptive
    and disproportionality analysis, time-to-onset analysis, network
    analysis, retrieval algorithms, and visualization.
